text: Dilmai Saiske is a Palauan politician, who has been a member of the House of Delegates of Palau since 2016 for the state of Ngarchelong. Prior to her election, Saiske worked in education for 25 years; she had previously stood for office unsuccessfully. ==References== Category:Living people Category:21st-century women politicians Category:Members of the House of Delegates of Palau Category:Palauan women in politics Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
